-- Weather to Benefit Corn Harvest in Brazil This Week
-- B y   M a r i o   S e r g i o   L i m a
-- 2012-07-09T13:20:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-09/weather-to-benefit-corn-harvest-in-brazil-this-week.html
Corn growers in  Brazil , the third-
largest producer behind the U.S. and China, will have little
rain and no frost this week, which should help the harvest and
final development of the grain, Somar Meteorologia said in an e-
mailed report today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mario Sergio Lima in Brasilia Newsroom at 
 mlima11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Attwood at 
